<li id="cite_note-2"><b><a href="#cite_ref-2" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.telegraph.co.uk/opinion/main.jhtml?xml=/opinion/2004/01/04/do0410.xml" class="external text" title="http://www.telegraph.co.uk/opinion/main.jhtml?xml=/opinion/2004/01/04/do0410.xml" rel="nofollow">Daily Telegraph profile</a></li>
